These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, blues, salsa, house
1. the fan of blues is between the fan of salsa and the fan of house##2
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of rock is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | rock | house | blues | salsa |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, lemonade, water, juice
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | juice | coffee | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard, hedgehog, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the frog##2
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | frog | hedgehog | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, pomegranate, plum, avocado
1. the person eating plum is between the person eating pomegranate and the person eating grapefruit##2
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating plum##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food   | avocado | pomegranate | plum | grapefruit |

 #################################

 
